      "comment": "SKINNY MARIE (8) ran below best last time finishing seventh (23.79) over 400m at this track from Box 2. Boasts three wins from five starts out of this box. Tough to beat if on-song. IRON LADY (2) found trouble in the run at this course and distance last time and failed to finish. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Bold showing expected on best. GUNNELL GIRL (1) finished second (17.58) two back at Taree Super Track but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and seven minor placings to her credit. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. STARLIGHT DUKE (6) is a last start all-the-way winner. Will be thereabouts.",
